<h1>Proposal for &quot;Config_Lite&quot;</h1>
<div id="nav">
  <ul>
    <li><a href="pepr-proposal-show.php?id=645" title="View proposal details">Main</a></li>
    <li><a href="pepr-comments-show.php?id=645" title="View and/or enter comments">Comments</a></li>
    <li><a href="pepr-votes-show.php?id=645" title="View and/or enter votes">Votes</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" style="width: 100%">

 <tr>
  <th class="headrow" style="width: 50%">&raquo; Metadata</th>
  <th class="headrow" style="width: 50%">&raquo; Status</th>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td class="ulcell" valign="top">
   <ul>
    <li>
     Category: Configuration    </li>
    <li>
     Proposer: <a href="/user/pce">Patrick Engel</a>&nbsp;    </li>
    <li>
     License: LGPL    </li>
   </ul>
  </td>

  <td class="ulcell" valign="top">
   <ul>
    <li>
     Status: Proposed    </li>


   </ul>
  </td>
 </tr>

 <tr>
  <th class="headrow" colspan="2">&raquo; Description</th>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td class="textcell" valign="top" colspan="2">
   <p>a lightweight and fast Config Class for &quot;INI-Style&quot; Configuration Files. <br />
Config_Lite is inspired by Pythons ConfigParser.</p>

<p>A &quot;Config_Lite&quot; file consists of  sections, &quot;[section]&quot;, followed by &quot;name = value&quot; entries.</p>


<h4 id="toc0">EXAMPLE</h4>
<p>The Config_Lite Pear Package:</p>


<pre><code>
https://github.com/pce/config_lite</code></pre>

<hr />
<p>A Configuration File: `test.cfg'<br />

<pre><code>

[general]
lang = de
appname = ConfigTest

[users]
email = john@doe.com
name = John Doe</code></pre>

</p>

<hr />
<p>Example to read `test.cfg':<br />

<pre><code><span style="color: #000000">
<span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php

</span><span style="color: #007700">require_once </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'Config/Lite.php'</span><span style="color: #007700">;

</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config </span><span style="color: #007700">= new </span><span style="color: #0000BB">Config_Lite</span><span style="color: #007700">();
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">read</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'./test.cfg'</span><span style="color: #007700">);

echo </span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">;

</span><span style="color: #FF8000">// create new Section with Key `count'
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">set</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'mailbox1234567test'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'count'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #0000BB">1</span><span style="color: #007700">);

</span><span style="color: #FF8000">// array get Section 
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">print_r</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">getSection</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'mailbox1234567test'</span><span style="color: #007700">));

</span><span style="color: #FF8000">// get value with default value 0
</span><span style="color: #007700">echo </span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">get</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'mailbox1234567test'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'count'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #0000BB">0</span><span style="color: #007700">);

echo </span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">;
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre>

</p>

<p>Another Example to save `test.cfg':<br />

<pre><code><span style="color: #000000">
<span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php

</span><span style="color: #007700">require_once </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'Config/Lite.php'</span><span style="color: #007700">;

</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config </span><span style="color: #007700">= new </span><span style="color: #0000BB">Config_Lite</span><span style="color: #007700">();
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">read</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'./test.cfg'</span><span style="color: #007700">);
</span><span style="color: #FF8000">// set `count' to 1
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">set</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'mailbox1234567test'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'count'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #0000BB">1</span><span style="color: #007700">);
echo </span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">;
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">save</span><span style="color: #007700">();

</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">read</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'./test.cfg'</span><span style="color: #007700">);
echo </span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">;
</span><span style="color: #FF8000">// set `count' to 0
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">set</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'mailbox1234567test'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #DD0000">'count'</span><span style="color: #007700">, </span><span style="color: #0000BB">0</span><span style="color: #007700">);
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">save</span><span style="color: #007700">();
echo </span><span style="color: #0000BB">$config</span><span style="color: #007700">;
</span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre>

</p>

  </td>
 </tr>

